48  // TODO ensure correctness
49  BaseGasDensity(double const dryBulbTemp, double const staticPressure, double const barometricPressure,
50  double const relativeHumidityOrDewPoint, GasType const gasType,
51  InputType const inputType, double const specificGravity)
52  : tdo(dryBulbTemp), pso(staticPressure), pbo(barometricPressure), g(specificGravity), gasType(gasType)
53  {
54  double const satPress = calculateSaturationPressure(tdo);
55  double rh = 0;
56  if (inputType == InputType::RelativeHumidity) {
57  rh = relativeHumidityOrDewPoint;
58  } else if (inputType == InputType::DewPoint) {
59  rh = calculateSaturationPressure(relativeHumidityOrDewPoint) / satPress;
60  } else if (inputType == InputType::WetBulbTemp) {
61  throw std::runtime_error("The wrong constructor for BaseGasDensity was called here - check inputType field");
62  }
63 
64  double const rhRatio = calculateRatioRH(tdo, rh, pbo, specificGravity);
65  po = (((pbo + (pso / 13.6)) - satPress * rh) * g + satPress * rh * rhRatio) / ((21.85 / (g * 29.98)) * (tdo + 459.7));
66  }
67 
68  BaseGasDensity(double const dryBulbTemp, double const staticPressure, double const barometricPressure,
69  double const wetBulbTemp, GasType const gasType,
70  InputType const inputType, double const specificGravity, const double cpGas)
71  : tdo(dryBulbTemp), pso(staticPressure), pbo(barometricPressure), g(specificGravity), gasType(gasType)
72  {
73  if (inputType != InputType::WetBulbTemp) throw std::runtime_error("The wrong constructor for BaseGasDensity was called - check inputType field");
74  double const satPress = calculateSaturationPressure(tdo);
75  double const rh = calculateRelativeHumidityFromWetBulb(tdo, wetBulbTemp, cpGas);
76  double const rhRatio = calculateRatioRH(tdo, rh, pbo, specificGravity);
77  po = (((pbo + (pso / 13.6)) - satPress * rh) * g + satPress * rh + rhRatio) / ((21.85 / (g * 29.98)) * (tdo + 459.7));
78  }

86  double calculateSaturationPressure(double dryBulbTemp) const {
87  double const C1 = -5674.5359, C2 = -0.51523058, C3 = -0.009677843, C4 = 0.00000062215701;
88  double const C5 = 2.0747825 * std::pow(10, -9), C6 = -9.0484024 * std::pow(10, -13), C7 = 4.1635019, C8 = -5800.2206;
89  double const C9 = -5.516256, C10 = -0.048640239, C11 = 0.000041764768, C12 = -0.000000014452093, C13 = 6.5459673;
90 
91  double const tKelvin = (dryBulbTemp + 459.67) * 0.555556;
92 
93  if (tKelvin < 273.15) {
94  double const p = std::exp(C1 / tKelvin + C2 + tKelvin * C3 + tKelvin * tKelvin
95  * (C4 + tKelvin * (C5 + C6 * tKelvin))
96  + C7 * std::log(tKelvin));
97  return p * (29.9216 / 101.325);
98  }
99  double const p = std::exp(C8 / tKelvin + C9 + tKelvin * (C10 + tKelvin * (C11 + tKelvin * C12))
100  + C13 * std::log(tKelvin));
101 
102  return p * (29.9216 / 101.325);
103  }
104 
105  double calculateRatioRH(const double dryBulbTemp, const double relativeHumidity, const double barometricPressure,
106  const double specificGravity) const
107  {
108  auto const pw = (calculateSaturationPressure(dryBulbTemp) * relativeHumidity);
109  return (18.02 / (specificGravity * 28.98)) * pw / (barometricPressure - pw);
110  }
111 
112  double calculateRelativeHumidityFromWetBulb(const double dryBulbTemp, const double wetBulbTemp,
113  const double cpGas) const {
114  double const pAtm = 29.9213 / pbo, nMol = 18.02 / (g * 28.98);
115  double const psatDb = calculateSaturationPressure(dryBulbTemp);
116  // double const wSat = nMol * psatDb / (pAtm - psatDb);
117  double const psatWb = calculateSaturationPressure(wetBulbTemp);
118  double const wStar = nMol * psatWb / (pAtm - psatWb);
119  double const w = ((1061 - (1 - 0.444) * wetBulbTemp) * wStar - cpGas * (dryBulbTemp - wetBulbTemp))
120  / (1061 + (0.444 * dryBulbTemp) - wetBulbTemp);
121 
122  double const pV = pAtm * w / (nMol + w);
123  return pV / psatDb;
124  }
125 
126  // dry bulb temp, reference static pressure, reference barometric pressure, gas density respectively
127  const double tdo, pso, pbo;

129  // gasDensity, specificGravity
130  double po, g;
131  const GasType gasType;

208  void establishFanInletOrOutletDensity(Planar & plane,
209  std::function<double (Planar const &, const double)> const & calcDensity,
210  double const mTotal, double const assumedDensity)
211  {
212  double calculatedDensity = assumedDensity;
213  for (auto i = 0; i < 50; i++) {
214  plane.gasDensity = calculatedDensity;
215  plane.gasVolumeFlowRate = mTotal / plane.gasDensity;
216  plane.gasVelocity = plane.gasVolumeFlowRate / plane.area;
217  plane.gasVelocityPressure = plane.gasDensity * std::pow(plane.gasVelocity / 1096, 2);
218  double fanInletOrOutletStaticPressure = plane.gasTotalPressure - plane.gasVelocityPressure;
219  double fanInletOrOutletGasDensity = calcDensity(plane, fanInletOrOutletStaticPressure);
220 
221  calculatedDensity = fanInletOrOutletGasDensity;
222  if (std::abs(fanInletOrOutletGasDensity - plane.gasDensity) < 0.0001) {
223  plane.gasDensity = fanInletOrOutletGasDensity;
224  plane.staticPressure = fanInletOrOutletStaticPressure;
225  return;
226  }
227  }
228  throw std::runtime_error("In PlaneData::establishFanInletOrOutletDensity - density iteration did not converge");
229  }
230 
231  void calculate(BaseGasDensity const & bgd) {
232  auto const calcDensity = [&bgd] (Planar const & plane, const double psx) {
233  return bgd.po * (bgd.tdo + 460) * (psx + 13.63 * plane.barometricPressure) / ((plane.dryBulbTemperature + 460) * (bgd.pso + 13.63 * bgd.pbo));
234  };
235 
236  flowTraverse.gasDensity = calcDensity(flowTraverse, flowTraverse.staticPressure);
237  for (auto & p : addlTravPlanes) {
238  p.gasDensity = calcDensity(p, p.staticPressure);
239  }
240  inletMstPlane.gasDensity = calcDensity(inletMstPlane, inletMstPlane.staticPressure);
241  outletMstPlane.gasDensity = calcDensity(outletMstPlane, outletMstPlane.staticPressure);
242 
243  flowTraverse.gasVelocity = 1096 * std::sqrt(flowTraverse.pv3 / flowTraverse.gasDensity);
244  flowTraverse.gasVolumeFlowRate = flowTraverse.gasVelocity * flowTraverse.area;
245 
246  double mTotal = flowTraverse.gasDensity * flowTraverse.gasVolumeFlowRate;
247  for (auto & plane : addlTravPlanes) {
248  plane.gasVelocity = 1096 * std::sqrt(plane.pv3 / plane.gasDensity);
249  plane.gasVolumeFlowRate = plane.gasVelocity * plane.area;
250  mTotal += plane.gasDensity * plane.gasVolumeFlowRate;
251  }
252 
253  inletMstPlane.gasVolumeFlowRate = mTotal / inletMstPlane.gasDensity;
254  inletMstPlane.gasVelocity = inletMstPlane.gasVolumeFlowRate / inletMstPlane.area;
255  inletMstPlane.gasVelocityPressure = inletMstPlane.gasDensity * std::pow((inletMstPlane.gasVelocity / 1096), 2);
256  inletMstPlane.gasTotalPressure = inletMstPlane.staticPressure + inletMstPlane.gasVelocityPressure;
257 
258  // step 7
259  fanInletFlange.gasTotalPressure = inletMstPlane.gasTotalPressure - totalPressureLossBtwnPlanes1and4;
260 
261  // steps 8 - 13
262  establishFanInletOrOutletDensity(fanInletFlange, calcDensity, mTotal, inletMstPlane.gasDensity);
263 
264  // calculating plane 2 inlet density and pressure
265  outletMstPlane.gasVolumeFlowRate = mTotal / outletMstPlane.gasDensity;
266  outletMstPlane.gasVelocity = outletMstPlane.gasVolumeFlowRate / outletMstPlane.area;
267  outletMstPlane.gasVelocityPressure = outletMstPlane.gasDensity * std::pow(outletMstPlane.gasVelocity / 1096, 2);
268  outletMstPlane.gasTotalPressure = outletMstPlane.staticPressure + outletMstPlane.gasVelocityPressure;
269 
270  // step 7
271  fanOrEvaseOutletFlange.gasTotalPressure = outletMstPlane.gasTotalPressure;
272  fanOrEvaseOutletFlange.gasTotalPressure +=
273  (plane5upstreamOfPlane2) ? -totalPressureLossBtwnPlanes2and5 : totalPressureLossBtwnPlanes2and5;
274 
275  // step 8 - iteration
276  establishFanInletOrOutletDensity(fanOrEvaseOutletFlange, calcDensity, mTotal, outletMstPlane.gasDensity);
277  }

325  Output calculate() {
326  // TODO barometricPressure = barometric pressure, what to do if barometric pressure does vary between planes ? pg
327  double const x = (planeData.fanOrEvaseOutletFlange.gasTotalPressure - planeData.fanInletFlange.gasTotalPressure)
328  / (planeData.fanInletFlange.gasTotalPressure + 13.63 * planeData.fanInletFlange.barometricPressure);
329 
330  double isentropicExponent = 1.4; // TODO what value to use for GasTypes other than Air ?
331  if (baseGasDensity.gasType == BaseGasDensity::GasType::AIR) isentropicExponent = 1.4;
332 
333  // TODO barometricPressure = barometric pressure, what to do if barometric pressure does vary between planes ? pg 61
334  double const z = ((isentropicExponent - 1) / isentropicExponent)
335  * ((6362 * fanShaftPower.getFanPowerInput() / planeData.fanInletFlange.gasVolumeFlowRate)
336  / (planeData.fanInletFlange.gasTotalPressure + 13.63 * planeData.fanInletFlange.barometricPressure));
337 
338  double const kp = (std::log(1 + x) / x) * (z / (std::log(1 + z)));
339 
340  planeData.flowTraverse.gasTotalPressure =
341  planeData.flowTraverse.staticPressure + planeData.flowTraverse.gasVelocityPressure;
342  for (auto &p : planeData.addlTravPlanes) {
343  p.gasTotalPressure = p.staticPressure + p.gasVelocityPressure;
344  }
345 
346  double const fanTotalPressure = planeData.fanOrEvaseOutletFlange.gasTotalPressure
347  - planeData.fanInletFlange.gasTotalPressure + fanShaftPower.getSEF();
348 
349  double const fanStaticPressure = planeData.fanOrEvaseOutletFlange.staticPressure
350  - planeData.fanInletFlange.gasTotalPressure + fanShaftPower.getSEF();
351 
352  double const staticPressureRise =
353  planeData.fanOrEvaseOutletFlange.staticPressure - planeData.fanInletFlange.staticPressure +
354  fanShaftPower.getSEF();
355 
356  double const kpFactorRatio = calculateCompressibilityFactor(x, z, isentropicExponent);
357 
358  // corrected variables
359  double const qc = planeData.fanInletFlange.gasVolumeFlowRate * (fanRatedInfo.fanSpeedCorrected / fanRatedInfo.fanSpeed)
360  * kpFactorRatio;
361 
362  double const ptc = fanTotalPressure * kpFactorRatio * std::pow(fanRatedInfo.fanSpeedCorrected / fanRatedInfo.fanSpeed, 2)
363  * (fanRatedInfo.densityCorrected / planeData.fanInletFlange.gasDensity);
364 
365  double const psc = fanStaticPressure * kpFactorRatio * std::pow(fanRatedInfo.fanSpeedCorrected / fanRatedInfo.fanSpeed, 2)
366  * (fanRatedInfo.densityCorrected / planeData.fanInletFlange.gasDensity);
367 
368  double const sprc =
369  staticPressureRise * kpFactorRatio * std::pow(fanRatedInfo.fanSpeedCorrected / fanRatedInfo.fanSpeed, 2)
370  * (fanRatedInfo.densityCorrected / planeData.fanInletFlange.gasDensity);
371 
372  double const hc = fanShaftPower.getFanPowerInput() * kpFactorRatio
373  * std::pow(fanRatedInfo.fanSpeedCorrected / fanRatedInfo.fanSpeed, 3)
374  * (fanRatedInfo.densityCorrected / planeData.fanInletFlange.gasDensity);
375 
376  double const kpc = kp / kpFactorRatio;
377 
378  double const efficiency = qc * kpc / (6362 * hc);
379 
380  return {
381  ptc * efficiency * 100, psc * efficiency * 100, sprc * efficiency * 100,
382  {
383  kpFactorRatio, fanShaftPower.getFanPowerInput(), planeData.fanInletFlange.gasVolumeFlowRate, fanTotalPressure,
384  fanStaticPressure, staticPressureRise
385  },
386  {
387  kpc, hc, qc, ptc, psc, sprc
388  }
389  };
390  }

394  double calculateCompressibilityFactor(const double x, const double z, const double isentropic) {
395  double assumedKpOverKpc = 1.0;
396  auto const & p1 = planeData.fanInletFlange;
397  for (auto i = 0; i < 50; i++) {
398  double const pt1c = p1.gasTotalPressure * std::pow(fanRatedInfo.fanSpeedCorrected / fanRatedInfo.fanSpeed, 2)
399  * (fanRatedInfo.densityCorrected / p1.gasDensity) * assumedKpOverKpc;
400 
401  // TODO how to get isentropic exponent for gas at converted conditions? section 9.4.1 step 2
402  double const zOverZc = ((pt1c + 13.63 * fanRatedInfo.pressureBarometricCorrected) / (p1.gasTotalPressure + 13.63 * p1.barometricPressure))
403  * (p1.gasDensity / fanRatedInfo.densityCorrected) * std::pow(fanRatedInfo.fanSpeed / fanRatedInfo.fanSpeedCorrected, 2)
404  * ((isentropic - 1) / isentropic) * (isentropic / (isentropic - 1));
405 
406  double const zc = z / zOverZc;
407 
408  double const ln1xc = std::log(1 + x) * ((std::log(1 + zc) / std::log(1 + z))) * ((isentropic - 1) / isentropic)
409  * (isentropic / (isentropic - 1));
410 
411  double const xc = std::exp(ln1xc) - 1;
412 
413  double const kpOverKpc = (z / zc) * (xc / x) * (isentropic / (isentropic - 1)) * ((isentropic - 1) / isentropic);
414  if (std::abs(kpOverKpc - assumedKpOverKpc) < 0.0000001) {
415  return kpOverKpc;
416  }
417  assumedKpOverKpc = kpOverKpc;
418  }
419  throw std::runtime_error("compressibility factor ratio iteration did not converge");
420  }

423  PlaneData planeData;
424  BaseGasDensity const baseGasDensity;
425  FanShaftPower const fanShaftPower;
